Package: OtsuFire
Type: Package
Title: Fire Severity and Regeneration Mapping Using Otsu Thresholding
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Natalia", "Quintero", email = "jane@example.com", role = c("aut")),
    person("Olga", "Viedma", email = "olga@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Hammadi", "Achour", email = "hammadi@example.com", role = "ctb"),
    person("Jose Manuel", "Moreno", email = "jm.moreno@example.com", role = "ctb"))
Description: 
    Tools to segment fire severity and vegetation regeneration using 
    Otsu thresholding applied to RBR/dNBR image composites, including mosaic 
    handling, polygon metrics, post-fire regeneration, DOY flagging, 
    and validation against reference datasets. 
    Designed for Iberian Peninsula fire history analysis.
